heading: 2. The 22nd day of November 2021 is appointed as the day on which the
text_raw:
2. The 22nd day of November 2021 is appointed as the day on which the 
Maritime Jurisdiction Act 2021 (No. 28 of 2021), other than sections 32 and 
33, shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

17 November, 2021. 

SIMON COVENEY, 

Minister for Foreign Affairs. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 23rd November, 2021.
